  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the complete repair of the abdominal wall at the level of the former incision with
      only a partial repair at the level of the hernia in patients with an incisional hernia after
      median laparotomy in a prospective randomized trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
